Happy Monday!  To make the start of the week cuter, here is some #AIart of my two maincoons flying through space in their rocket ship bed.  It's a running joke in my house that they are climbing to space when they hop into our loft, so I couldn't resist #cats #maincoons

images.alt:
This whimsical digital illustration features two adorable tabby Maine Coon cats voyaging through a stylized deep-space void. The felines are nestled within a glowing white, plush rocket ship bed, which is propelled by vibrant orange and red exhaust flames at the base. One cat looks forward with curious green eyes, while the other playfully raises a paw toward the stars.
​The background is a dreamy celestial landscape rendered in shades of navy and indigo. A brilliant white crescent moon hangs to the left, balanced by a large, ringed planet resembling Saturn on the right. Smaller planets, glowing nebulae, and twinkling white stars are scattered throughout the composition, creating a soft, storybook aesthetic.
